    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes an optimized mechanism for BGP route
   reflection, known as BGP route broker.  It aims to utilize the BGP-
   based IP VPN as an overlay routing protocol in a scalable manner,
   specifically for hyperscale data center network virtualization
   environments, commonly referred to as Software-Defined Network (SDN)
   environments.

	 </t>
